as.leap

Class LCGameAnalytics

  • java.lang.Object
    • as.leap.LCGameAnalytics

  • public class LCGameAnalytics
extends java.lang.Object
    The LCGameAnalytics class provides an interface to LC's game logging and analytics backend. Methods will return immediately and cache requests. That is, the request will be sent immediately if possible or the next time a network connection is available otherwise.
